{"tid":1601003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方稱民陣添馬公園集會最高峰有8440人","createTime":"2019-09-29T00:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T02:09:45.000Z","uid":209024,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"54a5ac0664aa67db436649af7994c75b063b65d2","tid":1601003,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"佔領運動五周年，民陣舉辦的集會基於安全考慮提前結束，召集人岑子杰估計集會有20至30萬人參加，形容人數遠超預期，警方就表示集會最高峰有8440人。<br />\n<br />\n在集會開始不久，夏慤道就有大批穿黑衫的市民，突然走出佔據馬路，警方先後舉起紅旗及黑旗警告，並宣布短期內清場。警方向民陣表達短時間內清場，因此民陣提早約45分鐘，於晚上8時半前結束集會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=58f96a9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&h=6a7bb3e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-20190929.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bea78ca6d1827d3410fcddecd9c2ddb56a6a93bc","tid":1601003,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"今次又引發第幾次數學難題？"},{"pid":"2a8e33ab6c0ebec09c4f868fa41625b18416da5d","tid":1601003,"uid":236171,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:18:02.000Z","msg":"已經唔係毅進制咁簡單<br />\n警犬跌咗入平衡時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4558a896c8dbb45b6a38436552517f9c28a316","tid":1601003,"uid":175256,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:20:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1476405dbaa468d392d7e60472b6ccd7100d212d","tid":1601003,"uid":59425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:21:14.000Z","msg":"黑媽媽，睇唔清楚嘛<br />\n撳掣咪撳少咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945785f7b770dd8068eb9c30b19190b5e427199e","tid":1601003,"uid":169391,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:21:19.000Z","msg":"添馬公園果然係一個神奇的公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4788a77b099a532f39127c1e5815695116a624f6","tid":1601003,"uid":68780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"其實班黑警講咩都冇人信，連藍絲都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca12c969ecc1964de186d03300f307d3daaf05d8","tid":1601003,"uid":31323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:26:54.000Z","msg":"合理吖 添馬八千個<br />\n海富夏愨十幾萬"},{"pid":"2149ae92b6beb1887360937ec3201a8c49e348d7","tid":1601003,"uid":47617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:31:24.000Z","msg":"上次撐警笑佢地都話自己40萬人😂😂"},{"pid":"894475b71f0b9b24b40b4696bf8a401659c910b5","tid":1601003,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80b01b27153632de3b558579e71bf9be9f668dd","tid":1601003,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"「去人化亅<br />\n冇當你係人"},{"pid":"f43d30aaee24afa4fb42b6ff72edb77eb2f326ed","tid":1601003,"uid":305010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"前日愛丁堡都話有9520人，添馬公園點會得8440人，毅進制真難懂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4b3aa7e0605a8a997b06556ee346b5dd2aea07","tid":1601003,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地其實應該睇下毅進制點人數 唔同政治立場 統計有咁大分別<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">同樣係添馬公園集會 大家都企滿左場地 黑警報出黎既數截然不同</span><br />\n<br />\n7月17日撐警集會聲稱有16.5萬人 黑警指有5萬3千人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rwvc5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rwvc5G.png&h=516f2e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月17日建制守護香港集會聲稱有47.6萬人 黑警指有10萬8千人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoWSrrh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoWSrrh.png&h=dc9250b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月28日民陣9.28集會宣佈有20-30萬人 黑警指高峰時間8440人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdNim0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdNim0U.png&h=58269cab&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nReference<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190630/mobile/bkn-20190630142700965-0630_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190630%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190630142700965-0630_00822_001.html&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=c055acf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190630/mobile/bkn-20190630142700965-0630_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/364859/反暴力集會-大會稱有47-6萬人出席-警方稱有10萬8千人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F364859%2F%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%8947-6%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%8910%E8%90%AC8%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=130df17a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/364859/反暴力集會-大會稱有47-6萬人出席-警方稱有10萬8千人</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=58f96a9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483122-20190929.htm&h=6a7bb3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483122-2